casebody.data:
No. 526. William A. Chapman et al., Petitioners, v. Montgomery Water Power Company. January 11, 1904. Mr. W. A. Gunter and Mr. G. L. Smith for petitioners. Mr. Edward A. Graham, Mr. Robert.E. Steiner and Mr. Horace Stringfellow for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United' States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
